  * rm README.Debian dir docs 
  * Licence determination:
       ARTISTIC                                             => artistic
       COPYING/README/LICEN[SC]E (first 10 lines) =~
                 /same terms as Perl/                       => perl
                 /BSD/                                      => bsd
                 /Artistic/                                 => artistic
                 /GNU (LIBRARY|LESSER) GENERAL PUBLIC LICEN => lgpl
                 /GNU GENERAL PUBLIC LICEN                  => gpl

